                        width="wrap"
                        height="wrap"
                        contentAlign="center">

                        <!-- description text -->

                            width="wrap"
                            height="wrap"
                            text="일이삼사오육칠팔구십일이삼사오육칠팔구십일이삼사오육칠팔구십"

                            textColor="#aaaaaa"
                            textSize="12"
                            maxLines="1" />

                </Column>

                <!-- main image -->
                <Image
                    width="0"
                    height="wrap"
                    weight="3"
                    aspectRatio="315:212"
                    marginLeft="11"
                    url="@image/mainImage" />
            </Row>
        </Box>
    </layout>
